            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## whispermax v0.1.2

- redesigned recorder ui with a cleaner live waveform and better transcribing motion
- redesigned settings and dictionary screens with calmer, denser layouts
- smoother transcript delete undo flow with cmd-z support
- more reliable pinned microphone behavior across reconnects and reboots
- safer recovery when recorder startup or model preload fails
